name: sa4_g49b_non_scl_qual_level_of_edu_by_occup_by_sex_census_2016
title: SA4-G49b Non-School Qualification-Level of Education by Occupation by Sex-Census 2016

legal.licenceType: Creative Commons Attribution 2.5 Australia (CC BY 2.5 AU)

abstract:
SA4 based data for Non-School Qualification: Level of Education by Occupation by Sex, in General Community Profile (GCP), 2016 Census. Count of employed persons aged 15 years and over with a qualification. Excludes schooling up to year 12. Excludes persons with a qualification out of the scope of the Australian Standard Classification of Education (ASCED). G49 is broken up into three sections (G49a-G49c) this section contains 'Females Graduate Diploma and Graduate Certificate Level Graduate Diploma Level Occupation Managers' - 'Persons Advanced Diploma and Diploma Level Advanced Diploma and Diploma Level Not further defined Total'. The data is by SA4 2016 boundaries. Periodicity: 5-Yearly.
Note: There are small random adjustments made to all cell values to protect the confidentiality of data. These adjustments may cause the sum of rows or columns to differ by small amounts from table totals.
For more information visit the data source: http://www.abs.gov.au/census.
